Genre: Comedy/DramaA Year in the Life is a four-part sequel to the much-beloved Gilmore Girls. The show is set almost 10 years since its final episode aired in 2007. Each of the episodes (seasons) gives a glimpse into the daily lives of the Gilmores. Lorelai is still trying to find a footing in her relationship with Luke while grieving the death of her father. Rory is travelling the world as a freelance journalist, stuck between a casual relationship with Logan and her actual boyfriend, Paul. The show revives its unique fast-paced dialogue paired with a loveable wittiness, while aiming to give viewers a much more satisfactory conclusion. Star Rating: 4